Roster Rules
1. Use the same display_name here as the in-shop card title.
2. Use numeric rarity only so pricing and shop odds stay easy to tune.
3. Keep scaling_summary short; the detailed formulas belong in the prop entry below.
4. implementation_status should change whenever tuning or behavior changes.
5. Add notes only for blockers, edge cases, or special UI/runtime requirements.

